OL,3,CPolice investigating after car driven
OL,4,Cinto takeaway in Newcastle
OL,6,FA takeaway has been left severely
OL,7,Fdamaged after a vehicle crashed into
OL,8,Fthe premises in the early hours before
OL,9,Fbeing abandoned nearby.
OL,11,FNorthumbria Police said officers were
OL,12,Falerted to a disturbance on Moulton
OL,13,FPlace, Blakelaw, shortly after 2am on
OL,14,FWednesday (22 April).
OL,16,FNew Eastend Diner was badly damaged in
OL,17,Fthe incident, with the metal shutters
OL,18,Fand windows having apparently been
OL,19,Fsmashed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
