OL,3,CPolice investigating after car driven
OL,4,Cinto takeaway in Newcastle
OL,6,FThe driver of the vehicle involved
OL,7,Ffled the scene and enquiries are
OL,8,Fongoing to locate those involved.
OL,10,FPolice and forensic officers have
OL,11,Fremained at the scene throughout the
OL,12,Fmorning to gather evidence at the site.
OL,14,FForensics officers could be seen
OL,15,Ftaking photos and placing evidence
OL,16,Finto bags amid their investigations.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
