OL,3,CPolice investigating after car driven
OL,4,Cinto takeaway in Newcastle
OL,6,FA Northumbria Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Shortly after 2am today
OL,8,F(Wednesday), we were alerted to a
OL,9,Fdisturbance at a premises on Moulton
OL,10,FPlace in the Blakelaw area of
OL,11,FNewcastle.
OL,13,F"It is understood that a vehicle had
OL,14,Fbeen driven into the metal shutters of
OL,15,Fthe property, causing damage.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
