OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776881467
OL,3,CPolice investigating after car driven
OL,4,Cinto takeaway in Newcastle
OL,6,F"The driver has then fled the scene,
OL,7,Fand the vehicle was later found
OL,8,Fabandoned nearby. Enquiries remain
OL,9,Fongoing as officers look to understand
OL,10,Fthe full circumstances surrounding the
OL,11,Fincident, and to locate those involved.
OL,13,F"Anyone with information is asked to
OL,14,Fget in touch by sending a direct
OL,15,Fmessage on social media or by using
OL,16,Fthe live chat or 'report' form on our
OL,17,Fwebsite.
OL,19,F"Those who can't contact the us
OL,20,Fonline, can call 101. Please quote
OL,21,Freference number: NP-20260422-0075."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
